2026-04-16 21:08:18 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '我是 Manager，收到新项目需求：**宠物健康记录App 产品设计，支持多宠物管理和疫苗提醒**。\n\n按照工作规范，我将严格按顺序执行四个步骤。先从 Step 1 开始——初始化共享工作区。\n\n---\n\n## Step 1 — 初始化共享工作区', 'reasoning_content': 'Let me analyze the task. I\'m the Manager, and I need to start a new project for a "宠物健康记录App" (Pet Health Record App). I need to follow the steps:\n\n1. Initialize shared workspace (init_project Skill)\n2. Use requirements_discovery Skill for requirement clarification\n3. Use notify_human Skill to notify Human to confirm requirements\n4. Complete this round and wait for Human confirmation\n\nLet me start by loading the init_project Skill first.', 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "init_project", "task_context": "初始化共享工作区，为新项目\\"宠物健康记录App\\"创建目录结构和邮箱。roles必须包含manager、pm、human。项目名称：宠物健康记录App。"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-28f2d2a4e1d1415a8ede3d8e6db76b11', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 4776, 'completion_tokens': 212, 'total_tokens': 4988, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 96}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'created': 1776344899, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-1cbd3741-063f-9ecb-8c91-08e9c030be52'}
