2026-04-16 21:09:05 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': 'Now I need to write the requirements document to the shared workspace. Let me create the needs directory and write the document.', 'reasoning_content': 'Now I have the requirements_discovery skill instructions. I need to:\n\n1. Analyze the project requirements for "宠物健康记录App" - supporting multi-pet management and vaccine reminders\n2. Identify missing information across the four dimensions (目标、边界、约束、风险)\n3. Write the requirements document to /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md\n4. Then notify Human using notify_human skill\n\nLet me first create the requirements document based on what I know and what\'s missing, then write it to the shared workspace.\n\nKnown information:\n- Project: 宠物健康记录App (Pet Health Record App)\n- Core features: 多宠物管理, 疫苗提醒\n\nMissing information (four dimensions):\n- 目标: What specific problem does this solve? What\'s the success criteria? (partially known - pet health tracking, but success metrics unclear)\n- 边界: What\'s in scope beyond the two mentioned features? What\'s explicitly out of scope?\n- 约束: Time constraints? Tech stack? Resource limits? Target platform?\n- 风险: Known risks? Uncertainties?\n\nLet me write the requirements document and then use sandbox to write it.', 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "write-output", "task_context": "将需求文档写入 /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md。需要先确保目录存在，然后写入完整的需求文档内容。"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-4a07382aaf3b46489df798cfe26a3744', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 5958, 'completion_tokens': 313, 'total_tokens': 6271, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 243}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 4927}}, 'created': 1776344946, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-47f39188-932d-9223-b179-ef74efb89efb'}
